## Vault Conventions

- **IDs are sequential** — notes use `ZTL-NNNN`, references `ref_NNNN`, tasks `TASK-NNNN`
- **Frontmatter is required** — YAML front matter with type, status, tags, created, modified
- **Links use wikilinks** — `[[ZTL-0001]]` or `[[Title]]` resolved by the system
- **Tags use domain/scope** — e.g., `ai/ml`, `engineering/architecture`
- **Content types** — note (standard/decision/knowledge), reference, task, log
- **Status lifecycle** — seed → sapling → evergreen (notes), open → active → done (tasks)
